	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Puzzle type beta changes II]]></title>
		<link>https://pedropsi.github.io/puzzle-type.html#RSS</link>
		<guid>https://pedropsi.github.io/puzzle-type.html?guid=2020-04-17</guid>
		<pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2020 07:06:05 GMT</pubDate>
		<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<img src="https://pedropsi.github.io/images/180/puzzle-type.gif" width="180" height="180" alt="Puzzle type" title="Puzzle type"/>
			
<p>Ongoing beta playtesting changes: the problematic DVO*** puzzle was made (slightly) less cryptic, the NOK*** space display was improved, minor tweaks to ANA***, MOR*** was fully redesigned and the clue in WEI*** changed to LAT***. Number input was allowed in a few levels where helpful. The total number of levels is now 28. Many thanks, <span class="name">Patrick Collin Eye</span>!</p>
	
		]]>
		</description>
		<category><![CDATA[Game]]></category>
<category><![CDATA[Puzzle]]></category>
	</item>
	

	<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Puzzle type beta changes]]></title>
		<link>https://pedropsi.github.io/puzzle-type.html#RSS</link>
		<guid>https://pedropsi.github.io/puzzle-type.html?guid=2020-04-10</guid>
		<pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2020 07:06:05 GMT</pubDate>
		<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<img src="https://pedropsi.github.io/images/180/puzzle-type.gif" width="180" height="180" alt="Puzzle type" title="Puzzle type"/>
			
<p>Ongoing beta playtesting changes: clue HOMEOMORPHIC became TOP*** (with new rules); CHERISHEDWOMAN became SHE*** (expanded ruleset, same logic); O** received a new keyword; NOK*** lost the backspace glitch; small CSS tweaks and spacebar inputs support. Many thanks, <span class="name">Plurmorant</span>!</p>
	
		]]>
		</description>
		<category><![CDATA[Game]]></category>
<category><![CDATA[Puzzle]]></category>
	</item>
	

